If you want to change feed_dict in every run, you can use a hook. Example is as follows:
```
class MyFeedHook(session_run_hook.SessionRunHook):
  def before_run(self, run_context): 
    return session_run_hook.SessionRunArgs(
        fetches=None, feed_dict=my-feed-dict-for-this-step)
```
